## Key Research Findings (for finance app copy/content)

- Future Super has the highest fees ($700/yr on $50k) and below-median returns historically
- Switching to a top industry fund could save $150k–$250k+ over a working life
- ART High Growth and Hostplus Shares Plus are the top 10yr performers (~10% p.a.)
- AustralianSuper Balanced has the best fee-to-performance ratio among large funds
- Higher unlisted/alternatives exposure correlates with higher returns but also higher fees
- The SG rate assumption is 11.5% (current) moving to 12% (future legislated)
- Australian benchmark data is from ATO 2021-22 Taxation Statistics

## How to Run the Research Tool

```bash
cd research/super-research
uv sync && uv run streamlit run app.py
# Opens at http://localhost:8501
```

